payload.message:
Dev server is up. I started `npm run dev -- --host --port 5173 --strictPort --clearScreen false` in `app`, and Vite is serving at `http://localhost:5173/` (also available on your LAN at the addresses shown).

If you want to stop it later, end the processes `cmd`/`npm`/`vite` from this run: `Stop-Process -Id 19572,10192,13464` (avoid stopping the other `node` pid 19080 thats running Codex).

content.text:
Dev server is up. I started `npm run dev -- --host --port 5173 --strictPort --clearScreen false` in `app`, and Vite is serving at `http://localhost:5173/` (also available on your LAN at the addresses shown).

If you want to stop it later, end the processes `cmd`/`npm`/`vite` from this run: `Stop-Process -Id 19572,10192,13464` (avoid stopping the other `node` pid 19080 thats running Codex).
